Improve memory diagnoser accuracy (#2562)
* ï»¿Added `AggressiveOptimization` to methods involved in measuring allocations. Warm up allocation measurement before taking actual measurement. Isolated allocation measurement. Changed some `RuntimeInformation` properties to static readonly fields. Removed enable monitoring in Engine (GcStats handles it). Removed `GC.Collect()` from allocation measurement. Sleep thread to account for tiered jit in Core runtimes 3.0 to 6.0. Updated MemoryDiagnoserTests. Block finalizer thread during memory tests. Disabled EventSource for integration tests.
* Use Monitor.Wait instead of ManualResetEventSlim.
* Swap IsWasm and IsNativeAOT declaration order.
